<h1>Near-Term Future of Component-Based Software Engineering</h1>

<h3>Component-based software engineering is expensive and
requires commitment from the organization in:
hiring, funding, training, mentoring, QA, metrics reporting,
monitoring and management oversight.
<p>
Training is crucial for the success of CBSE.
Component-based software project managers CBSPM may follow
several tracks in their education.<br>
